Package: conmon
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: OCI container runtime monitor
 Conmon is a monitoring program and communication tool between
 a container manager (like Podman) and an OCI runtime (like crun)
 for a single container. It handles logging, exit code reporting,
 and attaching to the container.
